<li><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Recreational vehicle expenses and insurances</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Annual land and property tax<br/> </span></li>
</ul> <p><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>Note:</b> It is important to ensure these are input in the correct category (Basic or Additional) in the calculators due to the comparison to HEM.</span></p> </td>
<td><p><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>Rental expenses include</b><b style="font-size: 10pt;">:</b></span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Strata and other body corporate fees</span></li>
